---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  path="/guitar-lessons"
  title="Guitar Lessons in McKinney, TX | Anthem Music"
  description="Guitar lessons in downtown McKinney for all ages and levels. Learn acoustic, electric, bass, ukulele, and banjo from experienced instructors. Book a consultation today.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center;">Guitar · Ukulele · Bass · Banjo</span>
      <h1 class="center">Guitar lessons in McKinney</h1>
      <p class="lead mx-auto center">From first chords to lead lines — learn guitar the right way, at your pace, with instructors who make it stick.</p>
      <div class="center" style="margin-top:1.8rem;"><a href="/schedule" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Consultation</a></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>Built around you, not a rigid curriculum</h2>
      <p>Every guitar student learns differently. Some want to strum campfire songs, others want to shred, and plenty just want to finally learn the instrument that's been sitting in the closet. We meet you where you are — building lessons around your goals, your interests, and the way you learn best.</p>
      <p>Whether you're a total beginner, a returning player breaking through a plateau, or a parent looking to get your kid started right, our instructors have the experience to guide you. We teach acoustic and electric guitar, bass, ukulele, and banjo for students of every age.</p>

      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature"><h3>All Ages</h3><p>Kids, teens, adults, homeschoolers, and students with special needs all welcome.</p></div>
        <div class="feature"><h3>All Levels</h3><p>From your very first chord to advanced technique and improvisation.</p></div>
        <div class="feature"><h3>All Styles</h3><p>Rock, blues, folk, worship, classical fingerstyle — whatever moves you.</p></div>
      </div>

      <h2>What a first lesson looks like</h2>
      <p>Every new student starts with a consultation: a quick one-on-one assessment where we get a feel for where you are, what instrument and size fits best, and what you want to accomplish. From there we build a clear, personalized plan — no pressure, no guesswork.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="container cta-inner">
      <div><h2>Start playing guitar</h2><p>Book a consultation and we'll get you set up with the right instructor and a plan to match your goals.</p></div>
      <a href="/schedule" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Consultation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-hero { background: var(--cream-soft); padding: clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem) 0; }
  .page-hero h1 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .narrow { max-width: 760px; }
  .narrow h2 { margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; }
  .narrow h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .narrow p { color: var(--gray); margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
  .feature-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 1.5rem; margin: 2.5rem 0; }
  .feature { background: var(--cream-soft); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.6rem; }
  .feature h3 { color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.15rem; }
  .feature p { color: var(--gray); font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 0; }
  .cta-band { background: var(--orange); padding: clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem) 0; }
  .cta-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .cta-band h2 { color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .cta-band p { color: var(--white); opacity: 0.92; max-width: 46ch; }
  .cta-band .btn-primary { background: var(--white); color: var(--orange-dark); }
  .cta-band .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--navy); color: var(--cream); }
  @media (max-width: 700px) { .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
